{"tid":1625661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[呼籲及投票以達成最大共識]  唔好搞其他銀行","createTime":"2019-10-05T07:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T13:17:31.000Z","uid":190320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"75ab6d19856322545223849c169637b20e7f38c8","tid":1625661,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T07:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>本身我係一個和理非 <br />\n我明白好多人係討厭中資機構而作出攻擊<br />\n但比國際社會知道係好反感<br />\n政府亦有口實去指責示威者為搶錢而攻擊銀行。<br />\n我希望大家唔好再攻擊中國銀行同中銀香港，<br />\n更加唔好攻擊銀行<br />\n<br />\n同時有好多退休人士及老人家係靠食銀行股息生活,<br />\n銀行股價下跌, 派息少左既呢班老人家會好慘,<br />\n希望收到1000個LIKE 以示同意及支持。<br />\n唔該大家對準林鄭月娥呢個垃圾。</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b08230df7d03e14abb0f3aba9e3f13ec37d7273","tid":1625661,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"你睇和理非講野幾漢奸共匪"},{"pid":"f91411f59ad19e5ce8d95870520bd2a679bd7912","tid":1625661,"uid":190320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b08230df7d03e14abb0f3aba9e3f13ec37d7273","tid":1625661,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"你睇和理非講野幾漢奸共匪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"講事實啫, <br />\n搞銀行為咩呢,<br />\n對成個運動無幫助"}]}